<div id="intro_div">
  <p>In the winter of 2013, a blog was established by a teen writing under the name “Bailey Simms.“ Little is known about the author’s actual identity.</p>
  <p>Among Ms. Simms’s blog posts is a completed serialized novel which has now been published as "Dead in Bed". Interspersed within the novel’s segments, blog updates describe events in the author’s life up to the spring of 2015. At that point, the posts abruptly stop.</p>
  <p>The complete blog has now been reproduced here on this web app. None of the original material has been altered. The contents are disturbing.</p>
</div>

<div id="intro_button_div">
  <%= link_to 'posts/2' do %>
